This home is one of a kind! From the large amount of bedrooms and entertaining space to the beautiful landscaped yard. This 2 story traditional style home offers you 6 bedrooms, 3 upstairs and 3 downstairs and a nice two car garage. This home has been completely renovated top to bottom. Are you a fan of older style homes but with the modern updates? This home is for you!
